{"tid":398602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父舉報啪針 25歲女割頸亡","createTime":"2017-09-13T10:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T16:04:15.000Z","uid":139720,"like":12,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8be7a63e2e124b9a428c54b864f610a464e58e","tid":398602,"uid":139720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:18:05.000Z","msg":"父舉報啪針 25歲女割頸亡<br />\n<br />\n北角電氣道115號一個單位的羅姓男戶主(48歲)，今日凌晨零時52分，發現女兒(25歲)「啪針」注射毒品，羅父大義滅親致電報警，警員到場調查期間，羅女突然情緒激動以鎅刀割頸。羅女隨後昏迷被送到律敦治醫院搶救，但終告不治。警員在場撿獲載有液體的針筒，未有發現遺書。初步調查顯示事件沒可疑，惟死因有待驗屍確定。"},{"pid":"51669037986e92fde37c504599ecd14be2f8ad36","tid":398602,"uid":31384,"like":10,"dislike":32,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:20:01.000Z","msg":"一家人點解唔可以好好地傾下"},{"pid":"fec6030e9bd62ebc760317cbe66c2b75542d453e","tid":398602,"uid":2889,"like":9,"dislike":102,"score":-93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"死前比同我做愛先啦"},{"pid":"cd15af7b7bd5b71c13794858bd995600ade447a1","tid":398602,"uid":47005,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:21:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一家人點解唔可以好好地傾下</blockquote><br />\n點鮮覺得人地無好地地傾過？"},{"pid":"850f371f705708fd71fde605ed5e0b6f44e77992","tid":398602,"uid":62409,"like":57,"dislike":15,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"究竟係個老豆 個女定個仔呀 好亂呀"},{"pid":"52194740f2d1e7b94669a30166fc31f47c069660","tid":398602,"uid":98659,"like":14,"dislike":65,"score":-51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟係個老豆 個女定個仔呀 好亂呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n閱讀理解攞幾？"},{"pid":"c60460350110c868a3e3d14c9ae7c36d7f383fb1","tid":398602,"uid":62409,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T10:22:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>究竟係個老豆 個女定個仔呀 好亂呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n閱讀理解攞幾？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170913/57204924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbre